  "summary": "This document is a competition announcement (bando di concorso) issued by the Italian Ministry of University and Research for the academic year 2025/2026, funded by the European Union’s NextGenerationEU program. Its main purpose is to outline the rules and procedures for awarding DSU benefits, which are financial aids for students enrolled in universities and related higher education institutions. Key topics covered include the duration and conditions for receiving benefits, eligibility criteria and exclusions, special rules for international students, and application deadlines and procedures.",
